query:
SELECT 
  id,
  customerId,
  vehicleId,
  messageType,
  status,
  sentAt,
  recipient
FROM reminderLogs
WHERE sentAt >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 7 DAY)
ORDER BY sentAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
